** REMEMBER: AMERICAN SPELLING ONLY! **


BOLD, ITALICIZE, UNDERLINE
<b><i><u>YOUR TEXT HERE</b></i></u>


CHANGE FONT COLOR
<font color=red>YOUR TEXT HERE</font>


CHANGE FONT SIZE
<font size=12>YOUR TEXT HERE</font>


CHANGE FONT FACE
<font face=verdana>YOUR TEXT HERE</font>

^ or combine: <font size=12 face=verdana color=red>YOUR TEXT HERE</font>


INSERT IMAGE
<img src="YOUR URL HERE" width="400" height="300">


INSERT LINK TO ANYTHING
<a href="YOUR URL HERE">YOUR TEXT HERE</a>


INSERT VIDEO (change the width and height numbers to something that works for you)
- get the Embed code from YouTube, Vimeo, etc.
- OR:
<iframe width="560" height="315" src="YOUR URL HERE" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>



Example of a hex code website: https://htmlcolorcodes.com/
